## Behavioral Data Analysis

Behavioral data (`.tsv` files) are publicly available via OSF:
https://osf.io/am6y7/

The R Markdown script `run_analysis.Rmd` reproduces all behavioral analyses presented in the manuscript. It requires the behavioral `.tsv` files as input and generates all statistical analyses and figures related to the behavioral data.

Before running the script, download the behavioral data from the OSF repository and place the files in the appropriate input directory.
